{"parentUuid":"ee155fcb-abbe-4dc5-9af5-bf84835e9bd4","isSidechain":true,"userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/allenbot/project/auto-trading","sessionId":"871024c3-eabd-4d36-89b0-da88af72fb64","version":"2.1.63","gitBranch":"main","agentId":"a3443412b64316c0d","slug":"streamed-wondering-engelbart","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01YXJkNroT4hrkbzmccbWTVE","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"完美。现在我详细汇报数据库内容：\n\n## gate1（初考）表结构与数据\n\n### 1. **gate1_summary** 表\n按时间周期统计通过/失败情况：\n- **字段**：`interval`（周期）, `total`（总数）, `passed`（通过数）, `failed`（失败数）, `pass_rate`（通过率）, `threshold_min/max`（交易笔数门槛范围）, `x_value`（K线/交易笔数的缩放因子）\n\n- **数据示例**（10个周期）：\n  ```\n  1m:   840组中700通过，通过率83.3%，门槛2104笔\n  5m:   840组中704通过，通过率83.8%，门槛840笔\n  1h:   840组中730通过，通过率86.9%，门槛136-200笔\n  1d:   840组中757通过，通过率90.1%，门槛9-15笔（通过率最高）\n  ```\n\n### 2. **gate1_1h** 表\n单条记录详情（combo_id为主键）：\n- **字段**：\n  - `combo_id` — 组合ID\n  - `strategy`, `coin`, `interval` — 策略名、币种、周期\n  - `total_trades` — 该策略产生的交易笔数\n  - `klines` — 该币种该周期的K线数\n  - `threshold` — 通过门槛（=K线数 / X_value）\n  - **`passed`** — 1通过/0失败（**核心字段**）\n  - **`reason`** — **通过/失败原因说明文本** ✅\n\n- **数据样本**：\n  ```\n  combo_id 325 | accumulationdistribution | ADA | 1h\n    total_trades=20, klines=68927, threshold=196\n    passed=0\n    reason=\"不通过: 20笔 < 门槛196 (K线68927/X350=196)\"\n  \n  combo_id 327 | adx | ADA | 1h\n    total_trades=1362, klines=68927, threshold=196\n    passed=1\n    reason=\"通过: 1362笔 >= 门槛196\"\n  ```\n\n- **统计**：1h周期中，共110条失败，730条通过\n\n### 3. **gate3_short** 表（长期目标——维度选择）\n- **字段**：\n  - `combo_id`, `strategy`, `coin`, `interval` — 基础信息\n  - `all_pnl` — 总收益\n  - **`selected`** — 1选中/0未选\n  - **`selected_dimensions`** — 该combo在哪些维度进入了TOP5（逗号分隔）\n  - **`reason`** — **选中/未选的原因** ✅\n\n- **数据样本**：\n  ```\n  selected=1: \"入选: sp_rest维度TOP5\"\n  selected=1: \"入选: sp_bounce,sp_sprint维度TOP5\"\n  selected=0: \"未入选: 13维度均排名TOP5以外\"\n  ```\n\n## 核心发现\n\n✅ **pass/fail reasons 已完整记录**：\n- gate1_1h 的 `reason` 字段记录了每个combo的通过/失败原因和数值依据\n- gate3_short 的 `reason` 字段记录了选中/未选的维度依据\n\n✅ **可直接供决策使用**：\n- gate1: 需要 ≥ N 笔交易才能通过（\"交易量验证\"）\n- gate3: 需要在至少一个维度进入TOP5（\"收益维度验证\"）\n\n✅ **可追溯性完整**：用户可以从 reason 反推为什么某个策略被淘汰\n\n---\n\n**目录结构**：\n```\nlab/results/\n├── gate_v3/gate_v3_report.db\n├── gate_v4/gate_v4_report.db\n└── gate_v41/gate_v41_report.db  (当前最新)\n```"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":4,"cache_creation_input_tokens":508,"cache_read_input_tokens":28050,"output_tokens":1152,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":508,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CYhhPqUYSiugZiWdx25uo","type":"assistant","uuid":"59176e37-be12-42c6-beb4-2574dc7f1aae","timestamp":"2026-03-04T08:07:51.282Z"}
